WEBVTT

01:52.110 --> 01:57.620
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.610 --> 02:01.930
[Episode 26]

02:27.150 --> 02:29.750
Are you doing this on purpose,
or are you blind?

02:30.970 --> 02:31.770
That's right.

02:32.220 --> 02:33.680
I'm doing this on purpose.

02:39.280 --> 02:39.840
I know.

02:40.660 --> 02:41.660
The sweet dew tea,

02:42.570 --> 02:44.360
lover's tea of Jing City.

02:44.470 --> 02:45.270
It's usually

02:45.600 --> 02:47.660
brewed by a woman for her beloved man.

02:48.560 --> 02:49.890
I didn't expect you to be

02:50.400 --> 02:52.150
so petty and calculating.

02:52.800 --> 02:55.030
You tried to trick Fan Yun
with the sweet dew tea.

02:55.030 --> 02:57.290
Good thing I found out in time. Otherwise,

02:57.290 --> 03:00.220
Fan Yun would have definitely
fallen into your trap.

03:01.310 --> 03:02.710
You have your principles,

03:02.710 --> 03:03.710
I have my rules.

03:04.190 --> 03:05.560
Besides, Fan Yun didn't feel that

03:05.560 --> 03:07.020
I was setting her up today.

03:07.470 --> 03:09.160
She made it very clear to me.

03:11.290 --> 03:12.550
What did she say to you?

03:14.590 --> 03:15.630
She said,

03:29.320 --> 03:30.650
"This tea is very good."

03:42.180 --> 03:43.530
Tea

03:43.560 --> 03:45.010
is just a cup of drink.

03:45.740 --> 03:47.000
It goes right through you,

03:47.000 --> 03:48.810
and you forget it after drinking.

03:48.810 --> 03:50.540
But what I'm giving her tonight

03:51.410 --> 03:53.410
will definitely be unforgettable.

03:58.720 --> 04:00.410
Enjoy your sweet dew tea.

04:00.430 --> 04:01.230
I'm leaving.

04:11.050 --> 04:16.149
[South Gate]

04:30.270 --> 04:30.750
Fan Yun.

04:33.190 --> 04:34.159
Qi Zheng.

04:35.600 --> 04:36.510
Qi Zheng,

04:37.240 --> 04:38.790
what's wrong with you today?

04:38.790 --> 04:40.590
One minute you ran off in a panic,

04:40.870 --> 04:42.830
the next you had Suyin call me here.

04:43.230 --> 04:44.470
What's going on?

04:45.310 --> 04:46.270
Well...

04:48.360 --> 04:49.490
Just now, you two...

04:51.040 --> 04:51.830
Did you...

04:53.040 --> 04:54.020
Just now...

04:54.370 --> 04:55.370
Did what?

05:00.040 --> 05:01.070
It's getting late.

05:01.070 --> 05:02.510
We have to hit the road tomorrow.

05:02.510 --> 05:04.770
If you have something to say, just say it.

05:06.630 --> 05:07.290
Never mind.

05:08.190 --> 05:09.360
I just haven't

05:10.270 --> 05:11.480
brought you to see

05:11.480 --> 05:13.040
the night in Yong City yet.

05:13.480 --> 05:13.920
Look.

05:15.000 --> 05:16.980
Compared to the day we first arrived,

05:16.980 --> 05:18.260
it's so quiet tonight.

05:18.570 --> 05:19.630
Don't you think so?

05:27.240 --> 05:27.830
Fan Yun.

05:29.390 --> 05:30.430
Give me a moment.

05:30.600 --> 05:31.190
Okay.

06:28.800 --> 06:29.550
Where did

06:30.270 --> 06:31.600
this come from?

06:31.600 --> 06:32.950
I had Zhu Luan and the others

06:32.950 --> 06:34.120
make it with the gunpowder

06:34.120 --> 06:35.940
we found in the Spirit Immortal Cave.

06:35.940 --> 06:37.020
Gunpowder?

06:38.490 --> 06:40.360
It seems this Spirit Immortal Sect

06:40.360 --> 06:41.560
is really dangerous.

06:42.510 --> 06:44.360
But it's so beautiful.

06:46.040 --> 06:46.820
Yeah.

06:47.100 --> 06:49.330
To think they could make
something so pretty

06:49.330 --> 06:51.190
from such a dangerous substance.

06:56.560 --> 06:57.890
It's really beautiful.

06:59.040 --> 07:00.000
Qi Zheng, look.

07:01.000 --> 07:02.000
Although

07:03.010 --> 07:04.690
the obstacles ahead are real,

07:06.070 --> 07:07.070
so are

07:07.560 --> 07:09.830
these gorgeous fireworks

07:09.830 --> 07:11.000
before us.

07:11.920 --> 07:12.650
Come with me.

07:19.040 --> 07:19.600
Here.

07:20.890 --> 07:22.420
You're letting me light it?

07:44.670 --> 07:48.020
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

07:48.360 --> 07:52.020
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

07:52.590 --> 07:54.310
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

07:54.720 --> 08:00.270
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

08:00.650 --> 08:02.140
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

08:02.180 --> 08:04.520
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

08:04.680 --> 08:07.850
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

08:08.130 --> 08:10.350
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

08:10.370 --> 08:12.740
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

08:12.770 --> 08:16.470
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

08:16.780 --> 08:18.120
♪ For whom does ♪

08:18.140 --> 08:20.310
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

08:20.340 --> 08:24.310
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

08:24.540 --> 08:26.590
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

08:26.620 --> 08:29.010
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

08:29.100 --> 08:32.350
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

08:32.370 --> 08:33.860
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

08:33.900 --> 08:36.240
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

08:36.400 --> 08:39.570
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

08:39.850 --> 08:42.070
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

08:42.090 --> 08:44.460
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

08:44.650 --> 08:48.350
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

08:48.440 --> 08:49.780
♪ For whom does ♪

08:49.800 --> 08:51.970
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

08:52.000 --> 08:55.970
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

08:56.260 --> 08:58.310
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

08:58.340 --> 09:00.730
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

09:01.040 --> 09:11.440
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

09:26.890 --> 09:27.610
President.

09:27.630 --> 09:28.960
A secret report from Wu.

09:33.990 --> 09:35.140
[Secret report]

09:41.080 --> 09:43.030
[Praying matters leaked. Return at once.]

10:28.140 --> 10:28.970
Waiter.

10:30.030 --> 10:31.720
Has Mr. Zheng in this room

10:31.720 --> 10:32.550
checked out?

10:32.570 --> 10:33.360
Yes.

10:33.380 --> 10:34.410
He checked out last night.

10:34.410 --> 10:35.670
It seems he had an emergency at home.

10:35.670 --> 10:36.670
He left in a hurry.

10:36.720 --> 10:37.760
An emergency at home?

10:37.760 --> 10:38.410
Yes.

10:40.380 --> 10:42.560
Could something have happened
to his family?

10:42.560 --> 10:43.230
Fan Yun.

10:45.240 --> 10:46.500
Why are you zoning out?

10:46.570 --> 10:47.370
Let's go.

10:52.870 --> 10:54.260
The carriage is ready.

10:54.280 --> 10:55.440
Get in the carriage.

10:56.030 --> 10:56.950
Get in.

11:01.660 --> 11:02.540
Okay.

11:04.030 --> 11:05.380
When we get back to Ling'an,

11:05.380 --> 11:07.110
I'll treat you to steamed buns.

11:08.910 --> 11:09.240
Okay.

11:11.340 --> 11:12.690
Your Excellency!

11:14.210 --> 11:15.280
Yun.

11:15.310 --> 11:16.120
Zhu Luan.

11:17.750 --> 11:20.030
Yun, thank you for coming to Yong City.

11:20.050 --> 11:21.590
Thank you for coming to Hulin County,

11:21.590 --> 11:22.920
and for coming to us.

11:22.960 --> 11:24.240
My family made this.

11:24.630 --> 11:25.480
I know you're leaving

11:25.480 --> 11:26.730
Yong City today.

11:26.920 --> 11:28.520
I don't have much to give you.

11:28.830 --> 11:30.470
Have this snack for the road.

11:32.520 --> 11:33.970
Thank you, Zhu Luan.

11:34.360 --> 11:36.600
You must remember what I told you.

11:36.620 --> 11:38.760
Keep helping the pharmacy save lives,

11:38.880 --> 11:40.120
and don't forget

11:40.150 --> 11:41.390
to study hard.

11:41.410 --> 11:43.870
I already know
what I want to be in the future.

11:46.200 --> 11:48.030
Let me guess...

11:48.050 --> 11:49.210
Do you want to be

11:49.240 --> 11:50.080
a physician?

11:50.950 --> 11:52.490
Let me guess.

11:52.620 --> 11:54.780
You want to be like Yun

11:54.910 --> 11:56.360
and become a teacher.

11:56.360 --> 11:57.480
Am I right?

11:57.860 --> 11:58.410
No.

11:58.440 --> 11:59.720
I want to be

11:59.740 --> 12:01.850
an official just like Yun

12:01.880 --> 12:03.030
and help others.

12:03.180 --> 12:04.700
I will study hard.

12:04.910 --> 12:06.910
One day, I will be like you two.

12:07.360 --> 12:08.790
So until then,

12:08.870 --> 12:10.360
you must wait for me.

12:11.910 --> 12:12.630
Okay.

12:12.630 --> 12:14.420
We will definitely
wait for you in Ling'an.

12:14.420 --> 12:15.810
It's a promise.

12:16.110 --> 12:17.270
It's a promise.

12:46.310 --> 12:48.040
[Peace and Harmony]

14:08.840 --> 14:12.430
Farewell, Your Excellency.

14:14.450 --> 14:18.940
Farewell, Lady Fan Yun.

14:19.480 --> 14:22.860
Farewell, Your Excellency.

14:23.070 --> 14:27.640
Farewell, Lady Fan Yun.

14:29.150 --> 14:31.150
Farewell, Your Excellency.

14:33.030 --> 14:35.080
Farewell, Lady Fan Yun.

14:35.520 --> 14:38.400
Time to see the lords off!

14:54.030 --> 14:59.840
The Governor of Nine Cities is renowned.

14:59.860 --> 15:05.450
He cares for the people with benevolence.

15:05.480 --> 15:11.080
Lady Fan Yun is insightful.

15:11.100 --> 15:16.740
She risks her life to save the people.

15:16.790 --> 15:22.240
They destroyed fake drugs, bringing peace.

15:22.240 --> 15:27.630
They united against the epidemic
and assured the citizens.

15:27.630 --> 15:33.080
Grab your tools and let's shout together.

15:33.080 --> 15:38.480
Keep illness away and reduce disasters.

15:38.480 --> 15:44.550
May our people be healthy and safe.

15:50.730 --> 15:51.920
Lady Fan Yun.

15:52.700 --> 15:54.420
The masses have witnessed

15:54.970 --> 15:56.430
what you've done for them.

15:58.870 --> 16:01.520
♪ Our hearts reach for the morning glow ♪

16:01.590 --> 16:04.070
Farewell, Your Excellency.

16:01.690 --> 16:05.150
♪ Our dreams fear no barren land below ♪

16:04.090 --> 16:07.760
Farewell, my lords.

16:05.800 --> 16:10.890
♪ What does it matter
if we fly against the wind? ♪

16:07.790 --> 16:20.220
Farewell, Your Excellency.
Farewell, my lords.

16:11.330 --> 16:13.910
♪ We vow to live up
to our youthful prime ♪

16:14.170 --> 16:17.980
♪ To walk alongside ordinary folks alike ♪

16:18.550 --> 16:21.480
♪ Sharing the same ray of light ♪

16:20.250 --> 16:21.410
Let's go.

16:21.650 --> 16:27.180
♪ Fear no strange land nor dim twilight ♪

16:22.710 --> 16:37.230
Farewell, Your Excellency.
Farewell, my lords.

16:27.360 --> 16:30.430
♪ All for this boundless world ♪

16:30.450 --> 16:35.560
♪ To wear a robe of radiant glory ♪

16:36.960 --> 16:42.550
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

16:42.740 --> 16:46.930
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

16:46.960 --> 16:49.090
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

16:49.290 --> 16:54.980
♪ Chase the light,
let our dreams unfold wide ♪

16:55.100 --> 16:59.320
♪ With bold resolve, ignite plain faith ♪

16:59.350 --> 17:01.210
♪ Light them up ♪

17:01.240 --> 17:04.970
♪ Let the weathered past ♪

17:05.109 --> 17:11.180
♪ Turn to countless beams
of light within my eye ♪

17:06.569 --> 17:08.589
[Hulin County]

17:11.210 --> 17:17.470
♪ Await the sight of you ♪

17:20.040 --> 17:21.900
Keeping the people safe and happy

17:22.510 --> 17:25.240
is the responsibility
of the Lord of Nine Cities.

17:25.650 --> 17:28.170
Today is the first time I've ever felt

17:28.200 --> 17:30.330
the satisfaction of being a governor.

17:31.040 --> 17:32.120
So,

17:32.140 --> 17:34.140
even if the road ahead is difficult,

17:34.400 --> 17:36.060
it's still a worthwhile trip.

17:48.980 --> 17:50.530
By the way, Your Excellency,

17:50.530 --> 17:52.160
before Zheng Shi left,

17:52.190 --> 17:53.600
did he say goodbye to you?

17:56.590 --> 17:58.250
Why would he say goodbye to me?

17:58.920 --> 17:59.860
Even if he did,

18:00.090 --> 18:01.550
it would just be nonsense.

18:03.350 --> 18:04.260
Nonsense?

18:05.550 --> 18:06.810
What kind of nonsense?

18:07.640 --> 18:08.640
Nothing.

18:08.660 --> 18:09.720
Don't mention him.

18:12.050 --> 18:14.850
But he just left quietly

18:14.900 --> 18:16.300
without saying goodbye.

18:17.480 --> 18:18.940
Did he really say nothing?

18:23.480 --> 18:24.580
He told me

18:25.060 --> 18:26.990
that you praised the sweet dew tea.

18:27.590 --> 18:28.620
What did he say?

18:29.100 --> 18:30.300
He told me

18:30.330 --> 18:32.260
that you praised the sweet dew tea.

18:34.420 --> 18:35.830
Your Excellency, speak louder.

18:35.830 --> 18:37.130
Speak clearly.

18:37.220 --> 18:38.620
What did he actually say?

18:42.680 --> 18:44.110
Zheng Shi told me

18:44.770 --> 18:46.700
that you praised the sweet dew tea.

18:46.960 --> 18:47.990
The sweet dew...

18:48.240 --> 18:49.580
Fan Yun, do you know

18:49.920 --> 18:51.030
what sweet dew tea means

18:51.030 --> 18:52.490
to the people of Jing City?

18:58.440 --> 18:59.400
I...

19:01.480 --> 19:02.640
Of course I know.

19:03.550 --> 19:04.610
Then why did you...

19:06.960 --> 19:09.360
I did say the sweet dew tea
was good that day.

19:09.600 --> 19:11.350
But there was a second half to that.

19:11.350 --> 19:12.810
He didn't tell you, did he?

19:13.720 --> 19:14.680
Whatever.

19:15.900 --> 19:17.730
I'm not that petty.

19:18.160 --> 19:20.400
First half or second half, doesn't matter.

19:20.400 --> 19:22.890
I didn't include him
in the fireworks show anyway.

19:22.890 --> 19:24.490
Don't say it, I won't hear it.

19:25.750 --> 19:26.160
Fine.

19:27.320 --> 19:28.160
Then I won't.

19:36.910 --> 19:38.430
The second half was...

19:39.570 --> 19:40.960
The second half was,

19:41.070 --> 19:43.030
although the sweet dew tea is good,

19:44.110 --> 19:44.970
I don't like it.

19:45.610 --> 19:46.880
I also told him

19:47.040 --> 19:48.120
that he and I

19:48.140 --> 19:49.470
are not on the same path.

19:53.220 --> 19:54.100
Besides,

19:54.550 --> 19:57.080
the people's worries
haven't been resolved yet.

19:57.080 --> 19:59.110
How can I be in the mood for romance?

20:00.030 --> 20:01.310
Don't worry, Your Excellency.

20:01.310 --> 20:02.240
Before we fulfill

20:02.240 --> 20:03.770
our pact to govern the city,

20:04.020 --> 20:06.420
I definitely won't consider these things.

20:30.450 --> 20:37.010
[Juyun Pavilion]

20:45.960 --> 20:46.680
Boss.

20:46.710 --> 20:48.220
Why did Grandfather
suddenly go to the temple?

20:48.220 --> 20:49.400
And how did the abbot reply?

20:49.400 --> 20:51.130
Tell me the details carefully.

20:51.350 --> 20:52.330
No need.

20:54.560 --> 20:56.660
I'll tell you myself.

21:00.410 --> 21:01.210
Grandfather.

21:01.540 --> 21:02.860
I just came back.

21:02.890 --> 21:05.690
I haven't had time
to pay my respects to you at home.

21:11.030 --> 21:12.600
Lou Qiyan.

21:17.510 --> 21:19.220
Where did you come from,

21:19.530 --> 21:20.990
and where are you heading?

21:31.950 --> 21:33.120
I...

21:33.900 --> 21:35.560
Just came back from Yong City.

21:37.000 --> 21:39.080
Are you going to do business?

21:47.510 --> 21:47.950
You...

22:08.290 --> 22:10.730
Give me a straight answer.

22:12.880 --> 22:14.550
Do you want to be

22:15.240 --> 22:16.790
Lou Qiyan,

22:17.880 --> 22:18.960
or

22:19.510 --> 22:21.000
Zheng Shi?

22:28.480 --> 22:29.310
Grandfather.

22:31.040 --> 22:32.500
My subordinates told me

22:33.830 --> 22:35.460
that the bandits
who seized the sweet wormwood

22:35.460 --> 22:36.670
use moves similar to mine.

22:36.670 --> 22:37.500
Shut up!

22:39.540 --> 22:40.860
You have no proof,

22:40.890 --> 22:42.090
so don't speak nonsense.

22:42.090 --> 22:43.210
I have to say it.

22:43.970 --> 22:45.170
Over the years,

22:45.200 --> 22:47.750
you've been away from the family,
alone in Ling'an.

22:47.750 --> 22:49.440
Though you hold a high position,

22:49.440 --> 22:50.750
it's only superficial glory

22:50.750 --> 22:52.410
with no real command of power.

22:52.680 --> 22:54.160
I understand

22:54.230 --> 22:55.700
the hardships involved.

22:56.410 --> 23:00.010
What do you know at your young age?

23:00.810 --> 23:01.770
Grandfather,

23:03.000 --> 23:04.270
my engaging in business

23:04.270 --> 23:06.130
is by no means belittling myself.

23:06.830 --> 23:07.920
For the future of our Zheng family,

23:07.920 --> 23:09.450
it's even more beneficial.

23:12.820 --> 23:14.510
I really want to be Lou Qiyan.

23:21.240 --> 23:23.170
Please understand, Grandfather.

23:40.080 --> 23:44.830
[Ling'an City]

23:48.880 --> 23:50.070
Finally home.

23:51.310 --> 23:52.310
It is home,

23:53.270 --> 23:54.800
but also a new battlefield.

23:55.550 --> 23:56.650
Are you ready?

23:58.000 --> 24:00.400
From the day I decided
to become a female official,

24:00.400 --> 24:01.450
I was ready.

24:13.990 --> 24:15.150
Gao Ran, Gao Ran!

24:15.680 --> 24:16.630
Gao Ran!

24:18.410 --> 24:18.960
Gao Ran!

24:27.160 --> 24:28.130
Brother.

24:28.150 --> 24:29.080
Did you see that?

24:29.610 --> 24:31.220
Gao Ran just smiled at me.

24:31.880 --> 24:32.880
At you?

24:34.810 --> 24:36.410
I think he smiles at everyone

24:36.700 --> 24:38.170
like that.

24:39.440 --> 24:40.070
No.

24:40.290 --> 24:41.530
In his eyes,

24:41.550 --> 24:42.700
there was only me.

25:26.320 --> 25:27.910
Gao Ran, you are so nice.

25:27.940 --> 25:30.070
I knew you couldn't bear to let me fall.

25:30.880 --> 25:31.600
Is that so?

25:34.960 --> 25:35.920
Did you get to use the straw hat

25:35.920 --> 25:37.640
I gave you on your trip to Yong City?

25:37.640 --> 25:38.510
No.

25:38.510 --> 25:39.790
Carrying a straw hat on a march

25:39.790 --> 25:40.850
is too cumbersome.

25:41.240 --> 25:42.070
You're lying.

25:42.070 --> 25:43.270
Then what is this?

25:44.640 --> 25:45.850
Miss Wei,

25:45.870 --> 25:46.860
it's getting late.

25:46.860 --> 25:48.080
You should go back and rest.

25:48.080 --> 25:49.050
I won't go back.

25:50.160 --> 25:51.160
I want to go back.

25:51.820 --> 25:52.400
Tell me,

25:52.750 --> 25:53.510
is this my straw hat?

25:53.510 --> 25:54.200
I said it's not.

25:54.200 --> 25:55.310
Tell me, is it my straw hat?

25:55.310 --> 25:56.080
You're mistaken.

25:56.080 --> 25:57.050
It's definitely my straw hat.

25:57.050 --> 25:58.560
-Let me have a look.
-You're mistaken.

25:58.560 --> 25:59.840
Let me have a look!

26:00.570 --> 26:01.920
-I said you're mistaken.
-Feeling guilty?

26:01.920 --> 26:03.240
You don't dare admit it, do you?

26:03.240 --> 26:04.600
You actually missed me a lot, right?

26:04.600 --> 26:05.730
Did you miss me a lot?

26:12.750 --> 26:13.800
Your Excellency.

26:14.060 --> 26:15.940
While you were in Yong City,

26:16.510 --> 26:18.200
I followed your orders

26:18.830 --> 26:21.230
and set up temporary clinics, pharmacies,

26:21.640 --> 26:23.700
and relief stations in Ling'an City.

26:23.960 --> 26:26.350
I also distributed all the sweet wormwood
in the warehouse

26:26.350 --> 26:27.610
to the added stations.

26:28.160 --> 26:30.510
Everything is running normally
in Ling'an City.

26:30.510 --> 26:32.510
No plague patients have been found.

26:33.240 --> 26:35.440
Thank you for your hard work, Lord Jiang.

26:35.440 --> 26:37.120
I have been back
from Yong City for a few days.

26:37.120 --> 26:39.200
Fan Yun, please elaborate on

26:39.350 --> 26:40.810
the follow-up control of the plague.

26:40.810 --> 26:42.080
The popularization of medicine

26:42.080 --> 26:43.610
has been greatly enhanced.

26:43.720 --> 26:44.960
The plague in Yong City

26:44.960 --> 26:46.760
has also been fully controlled.

26:47.530 --> 26:48.810
In just a few days,

26:49.240 --> 26:51.190
all trade and farming in Yong City

26:51.580 --> 26:52.580
can be restored.

26:53.070 --> 26:53.690
Well done.

26:54.830 --> 26:56.090
The plague in Yong City

26:56.310 --> 26:59.440
was brought under control
in such a short time.

27:00.240 --> 27:02.640
Lady Fan Yun
deserves much credit for this.

27:04.310 --> 27:05.480
Just get to the point.

27:05.480 --> 27:06.270
But,

27:06.720 --> 27:07.920
I also want to ask

27:08.680 --> 27:10.310
about the beacon tower incident.

27:10.310 --> 27:11.310
Your Excellency,

27:12.200 --> 27:14.040
do you remember it?

27:14.400 --> 27:15.330
Lord Zheng!

27:19.310 --> 27:19.980
Lord Zheng.

27:21.590 --> 27:22.880
Do you really think His Excellency

27:22.880 --> 27:24.610
is unaware of the robbery

27:24.830 --> 27:26.090
of the sweet wormwood?

27:26.330 --> 27:28.860
His Excellency
isn't holding it against you,

27:29.070 --> 27:30.870
yet you are being insubordinate

27:31.140 --> 27:32.410
and questioning him?

27:33.030 --> 27:35.790
It's not a matter
of whether you should ask,

27:36.470 --> 27:38.670
but whether you want to ask or not.

27:39.640 --> 27:41.090
Go on, Lord Zheng.

27:41.120 --> 27:42.020
Your Excellency,

27:42.020 --> 27:43.700
I faintly remember

27:43.880 --> 27:45.870
the promise you made to the officials

27:45.870 --> 27:48.830
at the morning assembly,

27:49.540 --> 27:52.840
that you'd handle it impartially
upon returning from Yong City.

27:52.840 --> 27:53.840
Your Excellency.

27:54.350 --> 27:55.780
The city has its laws.

27:57.290 --> 27:59.090
I implore you, Your Excellency,

28:00.310 --> 28:01.610
to keep your promise

28:03.290 --> 28:04.290
and punish

28:05.190 --> 28:06.560
Lady Fan Yun.

28:07.300 --> 28:10.260
Please keep your promise, Your Excellency.

28:17.650 --> 28:19.340
Are you trying to rebel?

28:20.190 --> 28:22.390
The plague in Yong City has just passed.

28:22.540 --> 28:24.750
Merits are unrewarded,
and faults are unpunished.

28:24.750 --> 28:26.350
There are more imminent matters

28:26.350 --> 28:27.410
that haven't been dealt with,

28:27.410 --> 28:29.100
and you are already teaming up against

28:29.100 --> 28:31.360
the hero who stabilized Yong City and me?

28:32.840 --> 28:34.980
A gentleman's word is his bond.

28:36.640 --> 28:37.640
Your Excellency,

28:38.600 --> 28:40.340
If you are unwilling to do so,

28:40.680 --> 28:41.640
then how will you

28:41.670 --> 28:44.900
face your officials in the future?

28:46.640 --> 28:47.750
Lord Zheng...

28:48.750 --> 28:50.160
You are going too far.

28:55.980 --> 28:56.980
Your Excellency.

28:57.710 --> 28:59.790
I lit the beacon tower without permission.

28:59.790 --> 29:01.340
It was indeed
an overstepping of authority.

29:01.340 --> 29:02.450
Please punish me.

29:03.590 --> 29:05.220
Fan Yun lit the beacon tower

29:06.160 --> 29:07.960
to save the people of Yong City.

29:08.640 --> 29:09.960
If she is punished now,

29:10.280 --> 29:12.770
who would dare to sacrifice
for the people in the future?

29:12.770 --> 29:13.850
Your Excellency.

29:14.570 --> 29:16.700
Fan Yun overstepped her authority today,

29:16.700 --> 29:19.600
yet she claims
it was for the people's will.

29:19.770 --> 29:21.000
What about tomorrow?

29:21.860 --> 29:22.930
What if

29:23.730 --> 29:26.250
she uses the people's will
as an excuse again

29:26.790 --> 29:28.680
and oversteps in other ways?

29:29.070 --> 29:30.670
If every matter is like this,

29:30.770 --> 29:32.280
and everyone is like this,

29:33.020 --> 29:33.740
then,

29:34.810 --> 29:36.260
Your Excellency,

29:36.670 --> 29:38.910
what will become of our rules?

29:38.930 --> 29:40.380
I'm afraid you may

29:40.410 --> 29:44.170
never face the officials again.

29:45.270 --> 29:47.560
Your Excellency, please reconsider

29:47.790 --> 29:50.040
and punish Lady Fan Yun.

29:56.000 --> 29:56.620
Guards!

29:59.150 --> 30:00.110
Take Fan Yun

30:02.010 --> 30:04.470
to the Interrogation Bureau
to await trial.

30:05.820 --> 30:07.450
Lady Fan Yun, please.

30:11.170 --> 30:12.500
I accept my punishment.

30:23.360 --> 30:25.560
We take our leave.

30:30.180 --> 30:31.180
Your Excellency!

30:31.200 --> 30:33.720
Your Excellency, Your Excellency!
